---
// src/components/about/Story.astro
---

<section class="py-24 bg-warm-50">
  <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center max-w-5xl mx-auto">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold mb-6 text-brand-900">Our Story</h2>
        <p class="text-brand-800/60 mb-5 leading-relaxed">Churchify started with a simple observation: parishes across Ireland needed a modern online presence, but the options available were either too generic, too expensive, or too complicated.</p>
        <p class="text-brand-800/60 mb-5 leading-relaxed">Generic website builders don't understand Mass times, sacrament pages, or parish bulletins. And hiring a web agency means ongoing costs with no guarantee they'll understand parish life.</p>
        <p class="text-brand-800/60 leading-relaxed">So we built something different — a complete parish website platform that combines beautiful design with the specific features parishes actually need. One product, one price, fully managed. No technical stress.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg">
        <img src="/john-s-lane-church-inside-st-augustine-st-catholic-popularly-known-as-dublin-ireland-35101065.webp" alt="Inside a beautiful Irish church" class="w-full h-auto">
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
